We’re 1 week away from Mother’s Day and @Candacemread has the perfect mocktail to toast to Mom at Sunday brunch! 🥂 Get ready to hit save on this yummy Sunshine Mimosa inspired recipe! 
MANDARIN ORANGE & PEACH MIMOSA RECIPE: 
- 3 oz fresh squeezed mandarin orange juice 
- 2 oz peach juice 1 tablespoon of simple syrup (optional) 
- Splash of non-alcoholic orange liquor (optional) 
- Top with faux champagne (or bubbles of choice) 
- Garnish w/ grapefruit wedge, orange peel & edible flowers
